bookTag:
In order to open
the button room,
you must enter 4
digits.

    _ _ _ _

The first two digits
are the sum of the
coordinates of the
cobblestone block
in the button room.

The last two digits
are the number of
buttons in the
button room.

Steps to open the
door:

o Turn the redstone
lamp on the wall on.

o Make sure aquar-
ium is turned off.

o Select Mr. Quartz's
favorite beverage.

o Enter the secret
code in the button
room.
